/* eslint-disable template-curly-spacing */
 
import {css} from "emotion";
 
import styleMemoize from "../../../utils/style-memoize";
import flaggedStyles from "../../../utils/flagged-styles";
// import {unitMath} from "../../utils/css-utils";
import getMenuVars from "./menu.var";
 
export default styleMemoize(function(flags/*,variation,size*/) {
 
  const menuVars = getMenuVars();
 
  const {
    labelOffset,
    labelBackground,
    labelTextColor,
    labelTextMargin,
    labelVerticalPadding,
    labelHorizontalPadding,
  } = menuVars;
 
  const styles = flaggedStyles(flags,{
 
    /*--------------
       Labels
    ---------------*/
 
    _: ()=>(css`
      background: ${labelBackground};
      color: ${labelTextColor};
      margin-left: ${labelTextMargin};
      padding: ${labelVerticalPadding} ${labelHorizontalPadding};
    `),
    vertical: ()=>(css`
      background: ${labelBackground};
      color: ${labelTextColor};
      margin-top: ${labelOffset};
      margin-bottom: ${labelOffset};
      padding: ${labelVerticalPadding} ${labelHorizontalPadding};
    `),
    floatingLabel: ()=>(css`
      padding: ${labelVerticalPadding} ${labelHorizontalPadding};
    `),
  });
 
  return styles;
});
